{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UgD3fFxd2zC4WRkKkq3pA4","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-24\n     2→\n     3→### 10-4-rust-provider — create-story (2026-03-24T09:14Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **Ambiguity in epic definition:** Story notes mention `'library'` AppType for Rust, but `AppType` union in `src/lib/stacks/types.ts` has no `'library'` variant — only `'generic'`. Followed actual code behavior (returns `'generic'`).\n     6→- **Bevy system libs:** Story notes mention Bevy detection for Docker system libs, but no such logic exists in current `dockerfile-template.ts`. Deferred to avoid scope creep.\n     7→- **Risk — workspace aggregation ordering:** No cross-provider ordering concern in the provider pattern; handled within Rust provider alone.\n     8→- **Observation:** All 27 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. No external system dependencies for unit testing.\n     9→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1d547185-a995-481d-9659-9279ed70f717","uuid":"ac46a096-bbd6-4839-8efa-f86e49c49e94","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:25:10.123Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-24\n\n### 10-4-rust-provider — create-story (2026-03-24T09:14Z)\n\n- **Ambiguity in epic definition:** Story notes mention `'library'` AppType for Rust, but `AppType` union in `src/lib/stacks/types.ts` has no `'library'` variant — only `'generic'`. Followed actual code behavior (returns `'generic'`).\n- **Bevy system libs:** Story notes mention Bevy detection for Docker system libs, but no such logic exists in current `dockerfile-template.ts`. Deferred to avoid scope creep.\n- **Risk — workspace aggregation ordering:** No cross-provider ordering concern in the provider pattern; handled within Rust provider alone.\n- **Observation:** All 27 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. No external system dependencies for unit testing.\n","numLines":9,"startLine":1,"totalLines":9}}}
