rdering:** No cross-provider ordering concern in the provider pattern; handled within Rust provider alone.\n- **Observation:** All 27 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. No external system dependencies for unit testing.\n\n### 10-4-rust-provider — dev-story (2026-03-24T09:24Z)\n\nNo issues reported. 55/55 new tests pass, 3397/3397 total tests pass, no regressions.\n","numLines":13,"startLine":1,"totalLines":13}}}
