led within Rust provider alone.\n- **Observation:** All 27 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. No external system dependencies for unit testing.\n\n### 10-4-rust-provider — dev-story (2026-03-24T09:24Z)\n\nNo issues reported. 55/55 new tests pass, 3397/3397 total tests pass, no regressions.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":10,"oldLines":3,"newStart":10,"newLines":11,"lines":[" ### 10-4-rust-provider — dev-story (2026-03-24T09:24Z)"," "," No issues reported. 55/55 new tests pass, 3397/3397 total tests pass, no regressions.","+","+### 10-4-rust-provider — code-review (2026-03-24T09:34Z)","+","+- **MEDIUM (fixed):** Misleading JSDoc in `hasCargoDep` — example was backwards.","+- **MEDIUM (fixed):** Missing false-positive prevention tests for crate substring matching (2 tests added).","+- **LOW (not fixed):** `hasCargoDep` matches commented-out dependencies. Pre-existing behavior from `stack-detect.ts`.","+- **LOW (not fixed):** `getCargoDepsSection` doesn't handle `[dependencies.foo]` subsection format. Pre-existing behavior.","+- **Coverage gap:** No integration test for `installOtlp` success path (requires `cargo` binary)."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
