{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_015S9GdwyLtuVFuXDG4Q2a9G","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018j5KRxmJgNGZdBEpXdyQ1S","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/verification/10-4-rust-provider-proof.md","content":"# Verification Proof: 10-4-rust-provider\n\n**Story:** Implement RustProvider\n**Verification tier:** unit-testable\n**Date:** 2026-03-24\n**Verifier:** harness-run (unit-testable flow)\n\n## Evidence Summary\n\n- **Build:** `npm run build` — success\n- **Tests:** 3399/3399 pass (57 Rust-specific), 0 regressions\n- **Coverage:** 97.13% overall (target: 90%), all files above 80% floor\n\n---\n\n## AC 1: RustProvider implements all StackProvider methods\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n`src/lib/stacks/rust.ts` exists and implements all 14 methods: `detectAppType()`, `getCoverageTool()`, `detectCoverageConfig()`, `getOtlpPackages()`, `installOtlp()`, `getDockerfileTemplate()`, `getDockerBuildStage()`, `getRuntimeCopyDirectives()`, `getBuildCommands()`, `getTestCommands()`, `getSemgrepLanguages()`, `parseTestOutput()`, `parseCoverageReport()`, `getProjectName()`.\n\nEvidence: `grep` found 28+ occurrences of these method names in `rust.ts`.\n\n## AC 2: detectAppType returns 'agent' for async-openai\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `detectAppType > returns agent for async-openai dep` passes (rust.test.ts).\n\n## AC 3: detectAppType returns 'server' for actix-web\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `detectAppType > returns server for actix-web dep` passes.\n\n## AC 4: detectAppType returns 'server' for axum\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `detectAppType > returns server for axum dep` passes.\n\n## AC 5: detectAppType returns 'server' for rocket\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `detectAppType > returns server for rocket dep` passes.\n\n## AC 6: detectAppType returns 'cli' for [[bin]] section\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `detectAppType > returns cli for [[bin]] without web framewo