ckerfileTemplate contains required directives\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `getDockerfileTemplate > contains required directives` passes. Template includes `FROM rust:1.82-slim AS builder`, `cargo build --release`, `FROM debian:bookworm-slim`, `USER nobody`.\n\n## AC 15: getDockerBuildStage contains build-rust stage\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `getDockerBuildStage > contains build-rust stage` passes. Contains `FROM rust:1.82-slim AS build-rust` and `cargo build --release`.\n\n## AC 16: getRuntimeCopyDirectives contains COPY --from=build-rust\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `getRuntimeCopyDirectives > contains COPY --from=build-rust` passes.\n\n## AC 17: parseTestOutput parses single crate output\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `parseTestOutput > parses single crate test result` passes. Input `test result: ok. 42 passed; 3 failed; 1 ignored` returns `{ passed: 42, failed: 3, skipped: 1, total: 46 }`.\n\n## AC 18: parseTestOutput aggregates workspace output\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `parseTestOutput > aggregates workspace output` passes. Two `test result:` lines (10+5 passed, 0+2 failed) returns `{ passed: 15, failed: 2, skipped: 0, total: 17 }`.\n\n## AC 19: parseTestOutput handles no match\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `parseTestOutput > returns zeros for unrecognized output` passes. Returns `{ passed: 0, failed: 0, skipped: 0, total: 0 }`.\n\n## AC 20: parseCoverageReport reads tarpaulin JSON\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `parseCoverageReport > reads tarpaulin-report.json` passes. Returns `78.5` from `{ \"coverage\": 78.5 }`.\n\n## AC 21: parseCoverageReport returns 0 if missing\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `parseCoverageReport > returns 0 if file missing` passes.\n\n## AC 22: getProjectName extracts name from Cargo.toml\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `getProjectName > extracts name from Cargo.toml` passes. Returns `'my-rust-app'`.\n\n## AC 23: getProjectName returns null without Cargo.toml\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `getProjectName > returns null without Cargo.toml` passes.\n\n## AC 24: getSemgrepLanguages returns ['rust']\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTest `getSemgrepLanguages > returns rust` passes.\n\n## AC 25: getBuildCommands and getTestCommands return correct arrays\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\nTests `getBuildCommands > returns cargo build and test` and `getTestCommands > returns cargo test` both pass.\n\n## AC 26: RustProvider registered in index.ts\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n`src/lib/stacks/index.ts` contains `import { RustProvider } from './rust.js'` and `registerProvider(new RustProvider())`. `getStackProvider('rust')` test passes.\n\n## AC 27: All tests pass with 0 regressions\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n`npx vitest run` — 3399 tests pass across 123 test files. 57 new Rust provider tests. 0 regressions.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Total ACs | 27 |\n| Passed | 27 |\n| Failed | 0 |\n| Escalated | 0 |\n| Pending | 0 |\n"}}
