vider alone.\n- **Observation:** All 27 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. No external system dependencies for unit testing.\n\n### 10-4-rust-provider — dev-story (2026-03-24T09:24Z)\n\nNo issues reported. 55/55 new tests pass, 3397/3397 total tests pass, no regressions.\n\n### 10-4-rust-provider — code-review (2026-03-24T09:34Z)\n\n- **MEDIUM (fixed):** Misleading JSDoc in `hasCargoDep` — example was backwards.\n- **MEDIUM (fixed):** Missing false-positive prevention tests for crate substring matching (2 tests added).\n- **LOW (not fixed):** `hasCargoDep` matches commented-out dependencies. Pre-existing behavior from `stack-detect.ts`.\n- **LOW (not fixed):** `getCargoDepsSection` doesn't handle `[dependencies.foo]` subsection format. Pre-existing behavior.\n- **Coverage gap:** No integration test for `installOtlp` success path (requires `cargo` binary).\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":18,"oldLines":3,"newStart":18,"newLines":10,"lines":[" - **LOW (not fixed):** `hasCargoDep` matches commented-out dependencies. Pre-existing behavior from `stack-detect.ts`."," - **LOW (not fixed):** `getCargoDepsSection` doesn't handle `[dependencies.foo]` subsection format. Pre-existing behavior."," - **Coverage gap:** No integration test for `installOtlp` success path (requires `cargo` binary).","+","+### 10-5-migrate-consumers-to-stackprovider — create-story (2026-03-24T09:43Z)","+","+- **Risk:** AC17 (`verify-prompt.ts`) compares `AppType` not `StackName` — could false-positive boundary tests.","+- **Risk:** AC16 (`teardown.ts`) accesses state field not local variable — migration needs state shape understanding.","+- **Risk:** `detectAppType()` export chain may break if `stack-detect.ts` deleted before re-export verified.","+- **Observation:** `otlp.ts` is heaviest migration target (~10 stack conditionals). `scanner.ts` had zero stack conditionals."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
